{"tid":659751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"10-5-2018，雲加憔悴，人痛心因你別去，我已不懂得哭笑 望著你身影遠去。","createTime":"2018-05-10T05:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T06:25:11.000Z","uid":36497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bcccd38319b7a359157b48c3ce60ec053c7e15","tid":659751,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/135828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F135828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=56b2afcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情憑誰來定錯對 我始終不想去追<br />\n寂寞路上遇痴心 雲加也有過痛苦一堆<br />\n<br />\n如能從頭遇見你 我始終不會後退<br />\n將雲加收於記憶中 仍沒法去剪碎<br />\n<br />\n濃情蜜意盡過去 凍好比一杯冷水<br />\n雲加默默望蒼天 心底裏滿載往昔唏噓<br />\n<br />\n迷雲已漸漸散退 過去的經已逝去<br />\n前路漫漫 顯得崎嶇 還是要雲加面對<br />\n<br />\n回憶起雲加的歡笑 是光陰沖洗不去<br />\n在這一生中 這一生中沉醉<br />\n<br />\n寂寞憔悴 這世界可有誰<br />\n逝去了的愛情陪雲加寄居<br />\n<br />\n雲加憔悴 人痛心因你別去<br />\n我已不懂得哭笑 望著你身影遠去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難得當天的雲加 是你我都傾出所有<br />\n令這一生中 這一生中無悔<br />\n<br />\n但雲加憔悴 這世界可有誰<br />\n逝去了的愛情陪孤單寄居<br />\n<br />\n雲加憔悴 人痛心因你別去<br />\n我已不懂得哭笑 就讓我消失告退<br />\n<br />\n雲加不懂得哭笑 就讓我消失告退<br />\n雲加不懂得哭笑 就讓我風中告退<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab253d8111ffcea31d3082084c51aae82d3bd45","tid":659751,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74084dac28a9c01fee52b23360f64898a8fa5e1f","tid":659751,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c494b3621e67aefa0eecff66fe6947424f5f65","tid":659751,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74084dac28a9c01fee52b23360f64898a8fa5e1f","tid":659751,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"雲加=英超校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efb9e83c315c81bb270d1f835916865c1aab473","tid":659751,"uid":161892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa53a6e0242a15e1647860e6b18f66900205e0bf","tid":659751,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"條賓周係你個嘴"},{"pid":"65269bd0f88ff6c6c36d2d95a9454282678596b5","tid":659751,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa53a6e0242a15e1647860e6b18f66900205e0bf","tid":659751,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"條賓周係你個嘴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"碌鳩裡也有你都閪水！"},{"pid":"46c70e4bd2f2e512869210601b149579b9ecbfb0","tid":659751,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"豬蛇飲水c源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}